{"tid":574769,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★\"Make IT YourCareer@SciencePark 2018」職業博覽 提供逾 1,000 個IT職位","createTime":"2018-02-27T16:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T16:49:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a7dcb66459644e09e687e09b8630b4863e6fcf9e","tid":574769,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T16:27:38.000Z","msg":"今年的科學園職業博覽「MakeiTYourCareer@SciencePark 2018」定於三月三日（星期六）舉行，進行招聘的企業涵蓋資訊及通訊科技、生物醫藥、人工智能、金融科技及設計等領域，提供科技研究、程式設計、市場營運等職位。<br />\n<br />\n職業博覽並非每項職位都要求應徵者有深厚的技術底子。流動應用程式開發公司 AppTech Director Edmund Lee 透露，他們去年透過科學園的職業博覽便聘請了<span style=\"color: red;\">沒有 IT 經驗的大學畢業生 </span>Iris 擔任助理項目主任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://preview.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/hkstp-career-expo-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fhkstp-career-expo-3.jpg&h=53fb9e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/02/27/hkstp-career-expo-2018/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2Fhkstp-career-expo-2018%2Flife-tech%2F&d=UZDbKUY8Pr2qvx8bfNpBp%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=bf042a5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/02/27/hkstp-career-expo-2018/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"263f0a496865ac4a9500c4e37e859951444bdc73","tid":574769,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T16:28:21.000Z","msg":"應徵者不但要有專門技能，亦要具備正面的性格特質。XGATE 今次便會聘請會計、社交媒體、銷售和編程的職位，業務發展總監 Andy Cho 表示，應徵者應有所堅持和表現積極，以及具備良好的溝通技巧；而 Fano Labs 溫豪夫則透露，公司著重「CRITIC」文化，即 Creativity（創意）、Responsibility（責任感）、Integrity（正直）、Tenacity（堅毅）、 Inclusivity （包容）和 Curiosity（好奇）。"},{"pid":"56f3fd751ea377e46bc346c1a04ef4d03be5546f","tid":574769,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T16:44:41.000Z","msg":"U go?"},{"pid":"e22a2867e2bc26ab99c477967ecef0f98106b525","tid":574769,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike"